  "description": "<p><strong>\u2022 RC Controlled :</strong>Experience the thrill of remote control with this RC stunt car. Its lithium battery-powered design ensures smooth and efficient operation.</p><p>\n</p><p><strong>\u2022 Gesture Sensing :</strong>This unique toy features gesture sensing technology, allowing you to control the car's movements with your hands for a truly interactive experience.</p><p>\n</p><p><strong>\u2022 Four-Wheel Drive :</strong>The four-wheel drive system provides superior traction and maneuverability, making off-road racing thrilling and fun.</p><p>\n</p><p><strong>\u2022 Light Music Feature :</strong>Equipped with a light music feature, this RC car not only provides visual entertainment but also adds a musical touch to your playtime.</p><p>\n</p><p><strong>\u2022 Age Recommendation :</strong>Recommended for children aged 6-12, this RC car is a perfect gift for those who love racing and technology.</p><p>\n</p><p><strong>\u2022 Off-Road Racing :</strong>Designed for off-road racing, this RC car can handle rough terrains, making it an ideal toy for outdoor play.</p><p>\n</p><p>otice</p><p>1. This toy is divided into dual control versions and single control versions. Single control refers to the product only being equipped with a handle remote control, while dual control refers to the product being equipped with both a handle remote control and a watch remote control;</p><p>2. Please choose to place an order based on personal preferences;</p><p>3. If you purchase a dual control version, when switching from a joystick remote control to a watch remote control, you need to turn off the joystick, turn off the toy car, and restart it. When the watch is turned on, it needs to be paired again. When switching from a joystick remote control to a watch remote control, it needs to be matched again according to the same principle.</p><p><span><span></span></span><span><span><span><span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><img src=\"https://c